## Configuring

The Qovery configuration file is placed in:

```text
etc/qovery/qovery.toml
```

A full spec is located at `/etc/qovery/qovery.spec.toml` and examples are
located in `/etc/qovery/examples/*`. You can learn more about configuring
Qovery in the [Configuration][docs.configuration] section.

